(2, 'Highlands 550085', 'highlands-550085', '550085-1', 15, 88, '<p>Nature wants to make itself at home. And it pulls it off brilliantly, with natural shades like this pale greige with a touch of iridescence. The grainy texture of the wallcovering is reminiscent of a ray, but also leaves room for a multitude of interpretations. And no wonder: there are so many different sides to nature.</p>', '2021-10-16 18:22:48', '2021-10-16 18:24:14'),
(3, 'Highlands 550153', 'highlands-550153', '550153-1', 15, 89, '<p>This wallcovering design in salmon leather is our latest catch. The scale-like patina has a highly authentic look, while its smoky grey and dark blue hue gives it a consummate elegance. A striped pattern provides subtle variation. It s just the thing for those who want to make their walls appear longer and higher.</p>', '2021-10-16 18:25:45', '2021-10-16 18:25:46'),
(4, 'Highlands 550146', 'highlands-550146', '550146-1', 15, 90, '<p>This wallcovering design in salmon leather is our latest catch. The scale-like patina has a highly authentic look, while its smoky grey and dark blue hue gives it a consummate elegance. A striped pattern provides subtle variation. It s just the thing for those who want to make their walls appear longer and higher.</p>', '2021-10-16 18:27:13', '2021-10-16 18:27:13'),
(5, 'Wallpaper Rasch Textil flower branch white gloss 227542', 'wallpaper-rasch-textil-flower-branch-white-gloss-227542', '227542', 16, 92, '<p>Rasch Textil represents with its wallpaper collection &acirc;&euro;&oelig;Jaipur&acirc;&euro; stunning designs which are influenced by cultures from all over the world. It seems that each wallpaper has its own story to tell. Thus, these wallpaper embodies a warm flair to your home. In doing so, the non-woven wallpaper 227542 fascinates with its flower and branch motif and bright colouration of white, anthracite and berry as well as noble gloss-effect. In addition, the Rasch Textil wallpaper is washable, dry strippable and has a good lightfastness.</p>', '2021-10-16 18:44:21', '2021-10-16 18:44:21'),
(6, 'Wallpaper Rasch Textil flower nature lilac grey 227566', 'wallpaper-rasch-textil-flower-nature-lilac-grey-227566', '227566', 16, 93, '<p>Rasch Textil represents with its wallpaper collection &acirc;&euro;&oelig;Jaipur&acirc;&euro; stunning designs which are influenced by cultures from all over the world. It seems that each wallpaper has its own story to tell. Thus, these wallpaper embodies a warm flair to your home. In doing so, the non-woven wallpaper 227566 fascinates with its floral motif and bright colouration of lilac grey, grey, berry and purple. In addition, the Rasch Textil wallpaper is washable, dry strippable and has a good lightfastness.</p>', '2021-10-16 18:45:16', '2021-10-16 18:45:17'),
(7, 'Highlands 550573', 'highlands-550573', '550573-1', 15, 99, '<p>Nicely done! This wallcovering design is interlaced with delicate lines, creating an elegant bamboo-like look broken by slender decorative seams. The interplay of pale gold and off-white transforms walls into truly striking features. Who could ask for more?</p>', '2021-10-17 18:08:52', '2021-10-17 18:08:52');

